criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of Systemic Lupus Erythematosus (SLE) according the American Rheumatology
             Association (ARA) and/or Systemic Lupus International Collaborating Clinics (SLICC)
             Criteria

          -  Free and Clarified Consent Term signature.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who have other rheumatologic diseases (rheumatoid arthritis, sjogren
             syndrome, fibromyalgia, ankylosis spondylitis);

          -  Systemic Lupus Erythematosus Disease Assessment Index (SLEDAI) > 5;

          -  Patients with malignancy;

          -  Patients who do not accept the study rules as time and/or follow-up exercise program
             time proposed;

          -  Suspected or pregnancy confirmation;

          -  Patients with Inability or unwillingness to understand and/or sign informed consent
